{
  "lesson": "WC-12-06",
  "audioMaster": "training/module12-settings/WC-12-06-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 252.918,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Open Settings, and look at the left rail.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 2.199,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "Four pages control who gets into Wash Central and what they can do once they're in.",
      "startS": 2.963,
      "endS": 7.509,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "Three of them sit together under Users and Security.",
      "startS": 8.418,
      "endS": 11.086,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "The fourth is filed somewhere you wouldn't guess, and we'll go find it.",
      "startS": 11.716,
      "endS": 15.333,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Open System Users.",
      "startS": 15.821,
      "endS": 17.24,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "This is the master list of everyone with an account.",
      "startS": 17.722,
      "endS": 20.408,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "Eight columns, and four carry the support work:",
      "startS": 20.712,
      "endS": 23.132,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "is the account active, does it use single sign-on,",
      "startS": 23.616,
      "endS": 24.724,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "when did it last sign in, and what role does it hold.",
      "startS": 25.263,
      "endS": 26.719,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "Email and phone are there to reach the person, not to fix the ticket.",
      "startS": 27.165,
      "endS": 34.204,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Read those four in order.",
      "startS": 34.662,
      "endS": 36.026,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Active tells you the account is switched on.",
      "startS": 36.778,
      "endS": 39.024,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "S-S-O tells you the password lives with the identity provider, not here.",
      "startS": 39.669,
      "endS": 44.039,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Last Login tells you when they last got in,",
      "startS": 44.807,
      "endS": 47.176,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "and a blank there means the account has never been used.",
      "startS": 47.528,
      "endS": 50.351,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "User Level is the thread you pull into the next two pages.",
      "startS": 51.341,
      "endS": 54.372,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "You won't scroll this list.",
      "startS": 54.824,
      "endS": 56.63,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Search by name, code, or email instead.",
      "startS": 56.63,
      "endS": 59.16,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "On the July eighth verified pass the tenant carried more than eight thousand accounts,",
      "startS": 59.16,
      "endS": 64.51,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "integration logins and the Micrologic support account included.",
      "startS": 64.51,
      "endS": 67.73,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "The search box earns its keep here.",
      "startS": 67.73,
      "endS": 70.615,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Now the page that hides.",
      "startS": 71.071,
      "endS": 73.711,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "User Levels controls how long a session lasts, so you'd expect it under Users and Security.",
      "startS": 73.711,
      "endS": 79.646,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "It isn't.",
      "startS": 79.646,
      "endS": 80.334,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "It's filed under Automation, a few groups down the rail.",
      "startS": 80.334,
      "endS": 84.065,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Open it there, and remember the spot, because every surprise-logout ticket ends here.",
      "startS": 84.065,
      "endS": 88.534,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Three columns here.",
      "startS": 89.22,
      "endS": 90.304,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "A name, a security level number, and a session timeout in minutes.",
      "startS": 90.944,
      "endS": 91.527,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Hold onto that number, it drives refunds on the next page.",
      "startS": 91.905,
      "endS": 95.426,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "The minutes are the answer for anyone who keeps getting kicked out.",
      "startS": 96.028,
      "endS": 103.163,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Read the timeout column.",
      "startS": 103.6,
      "endS": 105.127,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "On the July eighth verified pass, cashiers get five minutes.",
      "startS": 105.861,
      "endS": 109.634,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "So do Managers, Senior Managers, and the entry-level roles.",
      "startS": 109.854,
      "endS": 113.469,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Customer Service and the back-office levels get two full hours.",
      "startS": 114.122,
      "endS": 117.952,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "So a cashier dropping out mid-shift isn't a bug,",
      "startS": 118.446,
      "endS": 121.403,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "it's the level doing exactly what it was set to do.",
      "startS": 121.691,
      "endS": 124.376,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Back under Users and Security, open Security Level.",
      "startS": 124.813,
      "endS": 128.147,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "The link says Security Level, the page says Security Levels, same destination.",
      "startS": 128.75,
      "endS": 133.689,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Three columns: a name, a level number,",
      "startS": 134.477,
      "endS": 138.821,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "and the one support cares about, Refund Approval Required.",
      "startS": 139.105,
      "endS": 140.71,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Here's the gate.",
      "startS": 141.231,
      "endS": 142.018,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "On the verified pass, levels zero, three, and five needed approval before a refund could go through.",
      "startS": 142.49,
      "endS": 148.527,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Eight and above did not.",
      "startS": 149.043,
      "endS": 150.589,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "The rule underneath is plain: level five or below asks permission, eight or over just refunds.",
      "startS": 151.228,
      "endS": 152.827,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "One column settles most of these disputes.",
      "startS": 153.175,
      "endS": 160.547,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "Now tie the pages together.",
      "startS": 161.001,
      "endS": 164.381,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "A person's role sets their user level.",
      "startS": 164.381,
      "endS": 166.828,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Their user level carries a security number.",
      "startS": 166.828,
      "endS": 169.267,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "That security number decides whether they can approve a refund.",
      "startS": 169.267,
      "endS": 172.661,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "So a manager who can't refund isn't being blocked at random,",
      "startS": 172.661,
      "endS": 176.006,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "their level maps to a security number that requires sign-off.",
      "startS": 176.006,
      "endS": 179.046,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "Trace it in that order every time.",
      "startS": 179.046,
      "endS": 181.598,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "Last page.",
      "startS": 182.11,
      "endS": 182.925,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "Open Blacklisted.",
      "startS": 183.317,
      "endS": 184.736,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "These are plates the system refuses at the wash.",
      "startS": 185.437,
      "endS": 188.119,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "Four columns: the plate itself, the terminal where the block was set, who added it, and when.",
      "startS": 188.62,
      "endS": 194.931,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "This page answers one specific call.",
      "startS": 195.389,
      "endS": 197.782,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "When a customer swears their plate won't scan, look here before anything else.",
      "startS": 198.26,
      "endS": 202.657,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "If the plate's on the list, you can see who blocked it and when,",
      "startS": 203.511,
      "endS": 206.961,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "which turns a mystery into a two-minute answer.",
      "startS": 207.332,
      "endS": 209.76,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "One rule covers all four pages.",
      "startS": 210.16,
      "endS": 212.165,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "Each has a New Record button, and an admin can edit every list.",
      "startS": 212.165,
      "endS": 217.184,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "You only read them.",
      "startS": 217.184,
      "endS": 218.803,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p64",
      "text": "Passwords, levels, and blocks are changed by an administrator in production,",
      "startS": 218.803,
      "endS": 222.478,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p65",
      "text": "never from a support seat.",
      "startS": 222.478,
      "endS": 224.483,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p66",
      "text": "And when the account uses single sign-on, a password reset here does nothing;",
      "startS": 224.483,
      "endS": 229.062,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p67",
      "text": "that fix lives with the identity provider.",
      "startS": 229.062,
      "endS": 231.401,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p68",
      "text": "So, four pages, four questions.",
      "startS": 231.86,
      "endS": 234.434,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p69",
      "text": "Can they sign in: System Users.",
      "startS": 234.903,
      "endS": 235.794,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p70",
      "text": "Why do they keep dropping: User Levels.",
      "startS": 236.145,
      "endS": 237.139,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p71",
      "text": "Why can't they refund: Security Levels.",
      "startS": 238.217,
      "endS": 239.579,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p72",
      "text": "Why won't the plate scan: Blacklisted.",
      "startS": 239.967,
      "endS": 240.912,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p73",
      "text": "Learn where each one lives, and half your access tickets start answering themselves.",
      "startS": 241.746,
      "endS": 252.477,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}